\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Jiayu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Jiayu\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.804233640961614, \"rank\": 0.21980522489493343, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8056183942266936, \"rank\": 0.23169280808813406, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yang finished the competition in a season-best 1:25:54, topping the podium ahead of Spain's Maria Perez (1:26:19) and Australia's Jemima Montag (1:26:25).\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9053042602682297, \"rank\": 0.08081343362507531, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.994494163480787, \"rank\": 0.004525507485868165, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}, {\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"score\": 0.99985438789353, \"rank\": 0.00011862697880504, \"text\": \"Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\"}, {\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http: